Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.41,0:00:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忆往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德和哈里  抓鬼特工队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们属于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是专业人员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专业的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超自然事件调查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.96,0:00:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这东西  它能使我们获得一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名望  金钱  和姑娘...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滚床单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.98,0:00:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们之间的一切问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.27,0:00:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实都因为我们是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么  我们从此不再是家人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说既然你想好好合作  那就合作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说我们以后都公事公办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.09,0:00:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的公事公办是指你我之间的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那天说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你不在乎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.36,0:00:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能是没考虑周全
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.11,0:00:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我那么做  是因为那是该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并不是为了我而救我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是为了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.55,0:00:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fn方正黑体_GBK\fad(500,500)\b1\bord0\shad2\pos(193,233)\c&HE1DED9&}华盛顿州  斯普林代尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.70,0:01:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  你在家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,911  请问你有什么紧急情况
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我屋里有个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能说出你的地址吗  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.58,0:02:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士  请不要挂电话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开始追踪你的电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得保持通话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.68,0:02:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请保持通话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会派警官
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\bord0\shad1\fad(500,500)\fn方正准圆_GBK\c&H24EFFF&}凶鬼恶灵\N{\fs17\c&HFFFFFF&}第九季 第十五集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn方正水柱_GBK\fad(500,500)\bord0\fs22\pos(192,239)}{\c&HD2D2D2&}#瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.98,0:02:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.15,0:02:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,华盛顿州  我找到一桩案子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要我一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去猎魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你最近让我找不到北
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你想来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.56,0:03:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.23,0:03:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪现场流出的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩在自己房间被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门窗都锁着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壁画先生是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问得是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜  被拍下来的鬼魂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我像是要留下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fn方正黑体_GBK\fad(500,500)\b1\bord0\shad2\pos(193,233)\c&HE1DED9&}华盛顿州  斯普林代尔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我洗了好几个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得把地毯扯下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女儿  凯茜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地毯的颜色还是她自己选的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请节哀  迈尔斯太太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说凯茜没有什么敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你注意到发生过什么不寻常的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电路异常  灯闪烁什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视出毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有什么寒气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我想问一句
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要说到寒气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  听起来一定很怪  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而警方一无所获
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不得不卖掉房子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雇佣私家侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.11,0:04:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那些超自然论者打来电话时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超自然论者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道联调局会觉得这不合常理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:05:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这些人知道别人不知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠凯茜的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.09,0:05:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我至少要听听
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们提起寒气的事是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.28,0:05:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是超自然现象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们今天会过来看一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些超自然论者告诉你他们叫什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}抓鬼特工队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓鬼特工队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真见鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.75,0:05:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  我们又多了两个粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  哈里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是我们那次图书馆的采访
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.29,0:05:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.08,0:05:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐娜又发了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她改了她的头像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然裁过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.30,0:05:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但能清楚地看到有个男人搂着她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她还笑得那么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.42,0:05:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.17,0:05:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许他们只是纯洁的友谊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个搂着她的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温家兄弟  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-从没有人  -这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴听好  我们这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.12,0:06:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个小丑  给我钻进外面那辆破车里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.78,0:06:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后给我滚蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则我就打穿你们的膝盖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们需要点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以埋单了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张盘子上还有脏东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻去给我洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  特里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.33,0:06:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不怕你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我的枪打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.61,0:06:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在向我炫耀肚脐毛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是塞在裤子里的女枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两者都有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你们怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要处理这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-没错  -是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我看到的是一对儿为名利忘乎所以的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着摄像机拍摄一个刚失去女儿的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙计们  我们是调查员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们完全有权利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你们没有  知道为什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们只会碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者害死别的什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.98,0:07:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  你们要么识相点自己离开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么就爬出去  自己选
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐  你们能不能放松点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们心里有数
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-没错  -是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们其他的队员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个胖子哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.63,0:07:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有个女孩  有个女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.40,0:07:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们  我们不要他们了  他们是累赘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们绝对还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂了  现在就剩你们俩傻瓜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.08,0:07:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩不到五分钟就会死在鬼的手里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们以为是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-绝对不是鬼  -不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你们说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们觉得是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我来好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.25,0:07:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-行啊  -好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等这一刻等一辈子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:08:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃瘪吧  贱人们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.35,0:08:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会开枪毙了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贱人们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.43,0:08:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚刚说到  你们这就要走了  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈话愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.31,0:08:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看他们是蛋白质吃多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}捉鬼特工队  《瘦人揭秘》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德和哈里写了本书
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《瘦人揭秘》
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作者是美国最顶尖的超自然论者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.46,0:08:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这看上去的确像是凯茜·迈尔斯身后的那个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者被削掉脸皮的盖思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿呢  瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最早流传于网络的都市传说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会在目标生活的背景中徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.68,0:09:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到他决定下手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网上的一切都是真的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如鲨鱼袭击直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.67,0:09:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也写书讲那个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.29,0:09:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙计  不管是不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这网站上有几千人发帖了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人好像是新的大脚怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许瘦人只是名字新奇的鬼魂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么说是因为你真认为
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鬼魂还是单纯因为你讨厌捉鬼特工队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了  我们在凯茜屋里探测到了电磁信号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那房子旁边有电线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会影响读书
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个女孩死在密室里  萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,显然就是闹鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.58,0:09:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许它在房屋上锁之前进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢  迪恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎么可能世界各地的人们都看到了一样的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼魂可不会到处跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.44,0:09:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在隔界里各种乱套
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼魂说不定能满地出现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.74,0:09:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  迪恩  瘦人目击事件几年前就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔界的问题只有六个月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还到处有人说看见猫王了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.86,0:09:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是说那俩二货
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是任何方面的专家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查当地死亡名单
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看有没有谁可能是那个鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壁橱  凯茜度过生命黄昏的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  伙计  别再用脸书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟踪你的前女友了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没说错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把感情状态改为"一言难尽"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁管呢  是你甩了她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩的一切都一言难尽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她拿到奶油松饼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还非要扔掉里面的馅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是松饼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.74,0:10:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  她的确挺有病的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.38,0:10:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好了吗  -恢复状态了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就要找到瘦人了  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能闻到他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能闻到他的獠牙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未如此接近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:10.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这事真的很严肃  哈里  -是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温家兄弟也来了  你也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被萨姆和迪恩打穿膝盖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有考虑过或许我们该  别管这事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能让那俩肌肉男抢走我们的荣誉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.24,0:11:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁管他们怎么想  他们连推特都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会找到瘦人的  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我们的家人  和唐娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是为了让你前女友后悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了让所有黑后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛姬  斯布鲁斯  那些逃兵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想过什么"正常生活"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.91,0:11:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-去他们的  -太对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我们找到瘦人  是他们会上{\u1}《菲尔医生》{\u0}吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}脱口秀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.36,0:11:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们会上《菲尔医生》
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  开始录影吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.31,0:11:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好了吗  -嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.03,0:12:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个年轻女孩的闺房有两个用处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢笑和快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人将欢笑变成流血
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在气场太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你喜欢吗  -真的很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.79,0:12:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有很多女人喜欢上这个的  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会需要通气管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们将畅游在...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你们可能会渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  听上去很好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  过去六个月里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯普林代尔有三起非自然死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但都与凯茜·迈尔斯无关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且都不是很惨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的事应该不会产生复仇鬼魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有很多未解的死亡悬案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被归为瘦人所为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人死了  几周后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会发现死者的某张照片里有瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.65,0:13:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么瘦人是跟踪狂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据传闻是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傻子这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.26,0:13:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么没注意到这些被害人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是这些神秘死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以用非超自然原因解释
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.99,0:13:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些照片大部分看上去挺假的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括凯茜的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了凯茜的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.05,0:13:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯茜的照片没有修改过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.43,0:13:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她身后的那东西真的是在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这完全说不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这世上怎么能有东西又真又假
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.02,0:13:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个女孩死了  这个绝对假不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她做的最后一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用手机照了相
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张照片怎么流传到网上的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最早是发在一个瘦人粉丝网站上的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但IP地址却查不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西还有粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:13:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么肯定有人希望照片流传到网上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且肯定不是鬼魂上网发布的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警长在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想问他几个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警长去打猎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很感谢你们能来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是很需要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  你发现这个时它就被摔坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  或许她失手掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,911电话在11点59时断了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片发布的时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概凌晨2点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.38,0:14:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是验尸官认定死亡时间是午夜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她是怎么用手机发布照片的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是超自然现象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有几个人来过  问了些关于这案子的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说他们可能能帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们给了我一本他们写的书  关于...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:14:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}苹果餐馆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探员  谢谢你们能来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个二货在这儿干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得整点《灵媒缉凶》那套也没什么坏处
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们隔两个郡  大家在到处找一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8月份失踪的可怜的小男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警方找了一个灵媒去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天就找到了尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有监控录像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.00,0:16:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你们滚蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要把我赶出去吗  "探员"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在犯罪现场玩狗仔队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了对你们  对其他人有任何益处吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有博主  迪恩  那些信徒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些需要一些证明
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.33,0:17:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确信瘦人的确存在的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是说网上有很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这个瘦人很死忠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那可不是  -当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.87,0:17:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果加上适当的西藏字符
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.40,0:17:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩蠢货想没想过瘦人变成幻像怪成真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为几千人对瘦人的描述是统一的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于瘦人的传言千变万化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是幻像怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说废话了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.39,0:17:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们俩真的知道瘦人是什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.41,0:17:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我们只是在电视上扮演超自然论者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们完全不知道我们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们当然知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人是半人半树
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人认为他来自一个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.43,0:17:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自闭症男孩的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说你们也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙计们  过来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么从停车场突然进入餐馆的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门是锁着的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,录像显示特雷10分钟前才锁上的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁没锁都不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道瘦人能瞬间移动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的电磁探测器毫无反应
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许不是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二位探员也信这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-副警长  探员  干得好  -我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再看一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.46,0:18:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人把瘦人的餐馆视频
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发在我们博客的评论区了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-谁啊  -管他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持速度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么把忍者衣服穿上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能等到再出人命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚就要找到瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-在哪  -当然是林子里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.93,0:19:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太笼统了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据传说  瘦人在树旁边出没
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而林子里都是树
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.73,0:19:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两起命案  他肯定在本地的林子里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两个人死了  真的死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是忘不了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许该让萨姆和迪恩接手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再者  别再扫我的兴了{\fs14}[在我的彩虹上下雨]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有雨就没有彩虹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用科学对付我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.05,0:19:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一种情感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能现在放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们马上就能找到瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能弥补我们为了做这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而失去的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实交给专业人士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实也不是什么坏主意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是专业人士  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:19:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去树林吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便哪片树林  艾德  随便
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是病急乱投医  但说到瞬移
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想到"十字路口恶魔"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢捅人看视频网站的恶魔  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  说起那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特里被刀捅死的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经挂上网了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两千人看过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有人故意要让大家看到瘦人行凶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为会有人看  因为那些人很变态
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.51,0:20:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候病毒视频从小猩猩掉下树
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成杀手偷拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.66,0:20:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么视频会在网上疯传吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只可惜那个没留下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你五岁时扮成蝙蝠侠的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.50,0:20:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从棚屋上跳了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你以为自己会飞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时九岁  而且我扮的是超人好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球人都知道蝙蝠侠不会飞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时不知道  摔断了胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.51,0:20:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:20:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让你坐在我的车把上送你去了急诊室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是快乐时光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很重要的事要告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后这案子就归你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是哈里  一个人的抓鬼特工队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在在树林里调查潜在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人栖息地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.71,0:21:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人  深入树林
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.57,0:21:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离死亡之刃这么近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.03,0:21:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让人丧失理智
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸运的是  我清醒得很
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做抓鬼特工队  就专心一意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.42,0:22:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯布鲁斯想办公司
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.88,0:22:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛姬一心要玩轮滑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.82,0:22:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我凭什么阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.09,0:22:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是哈里  我不能让他屈服于他的女友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.25,0:22:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说抓鬼特工队很蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.17,0:22:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢  你们能相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不管
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.48,0:22:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她爸的对冲基金有多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.95,0:22:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能看着哈里变成公司的走狗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听起来像是碧池蒙德高中的悲惨时光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.87,0:22:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}取自电影Fast Times at Ridgemont High  雷奇蒙德的快乐时光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟案子有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.95,0:22:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里要离开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.87,0:22:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得给他一个留下的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我编造了瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人跟踪被害人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但局势反转了  朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.54,0:22:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟踪狂变成了被跟踪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.27,0:22:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说这破事根本就是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一张管家的老照片  后期好好处理一番
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我匿名发在一个恐怖论坛上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.01,0:23:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就火了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.25,0:23:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只我们伪造了一件案子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.60,0:23:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们准备收拾东西回家时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在网上说见到了瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.16,0:23:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我们就去追查  后来瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.02,0:23:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就成了大众传说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.90,0:23:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是领头羊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这感觉很奇妙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.77,0:23:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有追随者的感觉很好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里  非常沉迷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.33,0:23:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德  你得告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.50,0:23:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是追踪瘦人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.54,0:23:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有瘦人  我们就是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.52,0:23:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  蠢男
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.67,0:23:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.30,0:23:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我告诉哈里  他就会离开抓鬼特工队
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.16,0:23:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不告诉他  他还是会离开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.93,0:23:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.36,0:23:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密会毁掉两个人的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.89,0:23:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  等时机成熟我就告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:23:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在时机就很好  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.44,0:24:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他现在不在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.02,0:24:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在树林里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.93,0:24:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.95,0:24:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人  不管这是什么鬼东西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.41,0:24:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经杀死两个人了  现在哈里又只身在树林里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.60,0:24:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实算不上是树林啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.57,0:24:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让他在杂货店后面的几棵树边下车了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.51,0:24:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  他不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.57,0:24:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伙计们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.14,0:24:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  这是个  是个
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.61,0:24:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是个木棍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.29,0:24:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堆起来搭成的阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.95,0:24:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是瘦人留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.63,0:24:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.28,0:24:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.10,0:24:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.39,0:24:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.98,0:24:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这儿还有其他东西
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.57,0:25:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太紧了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.10,0:25:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.33,0:25:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我没事  -好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.15,0:25:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我们回旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.94,0:25:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再好好处理一下
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.32,0:25:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是对的  艾德  真有瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.01,0:25:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有新留下的胎痕
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.09,0:25:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我拍了照  -干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.09,0:25:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那辆车可能属于割伤你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.02,0:26:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,割伤我的是瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.35,0:26:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人不开车
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.29,0:26:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是瘦人  混球
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.75,0:26:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用我一一给你们解释吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.42,0:26:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你俩都挺聪明的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.26,0:26:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.83,0:26:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.40,0:26:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前怎么不说
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.00,0:26:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.19,0:26:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你会生我的气
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.26,0:26:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得没错  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.85,0:26:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.22,0:26:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在非常非常生你的气
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.72,0:26:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.16,0:26:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你毁掉了我们的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.62,0:26:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来要结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.29,0:26:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我离开她  跟你东奔西跑  生活在谎言之中
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.69,0:26:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少咱俩都在
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.36,0:26:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.29,0:26:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我没有编造瘦人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.20,0:26:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这会儿正做着无聊的工作  算着无聊的数字
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.35,0:26:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯唐娜爸爸之命是从
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.75,0:26:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救了你  老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.21,0:26:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我  免于什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.88,0:26:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免于过上好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.63,0:26:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免于不被刀捅伤
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.09,0:26:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还能再自私一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.42,0:26:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许现在还不晚
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.92,0:27:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以打给她试试
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.12,0:27:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-没用的  -也许能行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.36,0:27:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的  想知道为什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.10,0:27:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为已经有个男人搂着她了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.88,0:27:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的状态是"一言难尽"  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.14,0:27:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里  我们一开始并不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.58,0:27:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.51,0:27:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我是有一些内幕
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.80,0:27:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我们是为了粉丝坚持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.01,0:27:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟以前有什么不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.95,0:27:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们又不会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.83,0:27:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.06,0:27:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我颜面尽失  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.79,0:27:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里  我们可以熬过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.60,0:27:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以揭穿瘦人的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.00,0:27:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后继续抓鬼特工队的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.04,0:27:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.44,0:27:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不能相信你了  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.70,0:27:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  哈里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.61,0:27:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白  你生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.16,0:28:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所说的话都不是出自真心
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.72,0:28:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里  告诉我你需要什么
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.67,0:28:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.75,0:28:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以坐在这儿冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.52,0:28:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.14,0:28:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.18,0:28:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.88,0:29:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉被人胖揍了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.04,0:29:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一切都不是真的  萨姆
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.83,0:29:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德就是在装模作样  现在他还想要我假装
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.76,0:29:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像这一切没什么大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.54,0:29:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.71,0:29:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事你可以原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.54,0:29:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事不行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.13,0:29:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事算哪一种
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.31,0:29:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得自己考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.90,0:29:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胎痕找到匹配的了  如果你想...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.02,0:29:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.01,0:29:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种轮胎只有一种车用
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.48,0:29:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1989年的吉优都市
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.71,0:30:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么小的镇子  这车只有一辆
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.19,0:30:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官说是属于一个叫罗杰的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.39,0:30:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在镇子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.55,0:30:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北面的工厂做夜班保安
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.40,0:30:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西既可以瞬移  又有工作有车
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.33,0:30:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.27,0:30:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.33,0:30:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨姆和迪恩有线索了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.00,0:30:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们要去给你处理烂摊子了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.83,0:30:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对  是我的烂摊子
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.50,0:30:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该由我去处理
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.92,0:30:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只会越帮越忙
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.72,0:30:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.82,0:30:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不是没抛下他们不管过
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.39,0:30:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在何必自找麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.25,0:30:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再做水母的脊柱了  哈里
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.53,0:30:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水母哪有脊柱
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.26,0:30:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.36,0:30:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心碎和谎言以前
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.19,0:30:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的出发点是帮助人  对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.22,0:30:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.35,0:30:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.36,0:30:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们没道理不过去
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.33,0:31:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成我们主要的出发点
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.48,0:31:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里  我可以弥补这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.44,0:31:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以弥补这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.60,0:31:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是要跟我一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.37,0:31:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是说了  我和我的搭档会处理这事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.11,0:31:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我上司不在
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.37,0:31:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又没有搜查令
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.67,0:31:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事出了岔子  我可就麻烦大了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.38,0:31:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你在后面跟着就好
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.30,0:32:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想用用这些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.27,0:32:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你就是瘦人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.36,0:32:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不是那么胖
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.93,0:32:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也倒能说得通了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.19,0:32:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐  萨姆  让他住口
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.43,0:32:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.95,0:32:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什么  诺伍德
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.74,0:32:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是恶魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.61,0:32:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么瞬移进入餐馆的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.18,0:32:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团队合作
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.86,0:33:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没什么瞬间移动
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.81,0:33:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有几个白痴在造谣生事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.77,0:33:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我认得你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.02,0:33:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那家餐厅的服务员
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.18,0:33:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  你就是想杀了你老板吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.26,0:33:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特里是个人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.13,0:33:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那凯茜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.57,0:33:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她怎么惹你了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.59,0:33:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不愿意和我约会
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.57,0:33:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我用别的东西招呼她
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.48,0:33:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的刀子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.38,0:33:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好  罗杰
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.24,0:33:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来警长没活着离开镇子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.12,0:33:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该给我我要求的假期的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.37,0:33:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就为这个杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.87,0:33:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我谁也没杀
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.63,0:33:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是罗杰杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.15,0:33:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个疯子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.13,0:33:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我是个梦想家
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.84,0:34:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不怪你们轻视我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.88,0:34:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都轻视我
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.90,0:34:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅气的探员  来到这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.83,0:34:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就把我当成个小文员
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.37,0:34:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其实我就是"瘦人"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.37,0:34:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那种感觉有多棒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.38,0:34:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  变态  我还真不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.16,0:34:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  帅哥是不会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.02,0:34:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人无视是什么感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.34,0:34:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一个只有三百人的小镇长大
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.03,0:34:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从没有人注意过你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.59,0:34:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们看不见我们
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.07,0:34:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你俩是怎么认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.14,0:34:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过"疯子网"吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.60,0:34:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.86,0:34:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是两个呆子在一间空荡荡的酒吧相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.64,0:34:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一见如故
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.41,0:34:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和罗杰
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.09,0:34:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然都是阴谋论迷
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.39,0:34:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们发现了"瘦人"
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.24,0:34:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是就轰炸了整个留言板
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.20,0:34:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这算什么  变态角色扮演吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.60,0:34:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真人扮演
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.28,0:34:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发博客是很有趣  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.71,0:34:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  让我猜猜  你们想要更多
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.93,0:35:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道你们俩混蛋做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.05,0:35:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并没让你成为"瘦人"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.66,0:35:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们只能算是模仿犯
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.67,0:35:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是"瘦人"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.59,0:35:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你没办法告诉别人我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.05,0:35:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你马上就要死透了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.19,0:35:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戏开场
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.90,0:35:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你俩真是幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.79,0:35:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是我们目前为止最好的视频的主演
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.09,0:35:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等视频疯传
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.92,0:35:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都会知道"瘦人"是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.72,0:35:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备  开拍
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.11,0:35:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  别别别  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.27,0:36:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.38,0:36:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他踢到了我  这是报复
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.54,0:36:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是史酷比时刻  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.54,0:36:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}史酷比·杜  美国动画片角色
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.92,0:36:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱下面具
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.28,0:36:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不是瘦人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.45,0:36:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是个"咪咪"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.51,0:36:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德  应该是{\u1}弥母{\u0}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.51,0:36:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}文化传播中起基因作用的媒介  泛指模仿者
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.34,0:36:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可拼写是M-E-M-E
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.76,0:36:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二个E不发音
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.60,0:36:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是个咪咪  是个人类弥母
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.51,0:36:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我创造了你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.97,0:36:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢赐教
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.84,0:36:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我热爱经典  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.36,0:37:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正处于《弗兰肯斯坦》式的情节中
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.00,0:37:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然是我的创造者
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.89,0:37:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们本打算放你们中的一人一条生路
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.61,0:37:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来传颂我们的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.27,0:37:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可现在
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.68,0:37:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你们都死了  就没人能证明
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.90,0:37:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人是你们的创造
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.90,0:37:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.94,0:37:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开枪  不  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.91,0:37:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  冲我来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.28,0:37:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.75,0:37:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行吗  都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.11,0:37:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我枪里的子弹足够弄死你们俩了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.10,0:38:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-现场搞定了吗  -是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.10,0:38:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘦人的录像加上我摆放尸体的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.81,0:38:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该有足够的线索让别人以为
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.59,0:38:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是两个疯子同归于尽
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.71,0:38:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们只是凡人  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.97,0:38:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是恶魔  也不是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.67,0:38:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们  只是该死的凡人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.61,0:38:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  就像我说过的  人很变态
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.45,0:38:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们没事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.86,0:39:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我们不会和好如初了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.96,0:39:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做出了弥补
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.56,0:39:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们打败了那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.71,0:39:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是我们抓鬼特工队东山再起的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.54,0:39:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你来这是为了解决瘦人的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.52,0:39:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是想结束一个篇章  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.86,0:39:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是要结束这整本书
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.43,0:39:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你刚救了我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.87,0:39:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了人  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.12,0:39:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个坏蛋  哈里
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.87,0:39:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是个人  艾德
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.54,0:39:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多人因为你的谎言丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.07,0:39:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的谎言还不是为了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.69,0:39:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道为什么你看不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.11,0:39:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.68,0:39:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是为了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.32,0:39:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾德  我可以原谅很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.30,0:39:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这事我无法原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.10,0:39:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.23,0:39:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.37,0:40:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言难尽
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.33,0:40:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能载我一程吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.79,0:40:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.55,0:41:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里  你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.86,0:41:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.84,0:41:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说  不好
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.79,0:41:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和一个人一起混那么多年
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.92,0:41:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你甚至相信他会永远和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.96,0:41:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像  等你老了  在门廊喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.10,0:41:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会坐在另一把摇椅上
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.79,0:41:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可之后发生了些事
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.97,0:41:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.24,0:41:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一把椅子上的人不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.19,0:41:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂我的意思吗
